DUBAI: Bollywood megastar Deepika Padukone took to her Instagram account on Tuesday to announce that she is now the Global Brand Ambassador for Qatar Airways. For the latest updates, follow us on Instagram @arabnews.lifestyle The actress, a regular on the Cannes Film Festival red carpet, posted that she is “thrilled to be announced global brand ambassador for @qatarairways! Because there’s nothing else quite like it…” A post shared by Deepika Padukone (@deepikapadukone) In a clip shared on Instagram, Padukone can be seen enjoying lobster tail aboard a Qatar Airways flight, scrolling through the on-board entertainment system and enjoying Doha International Airport. Padukone is also the House Ambassador for Louis Vuitton, and the face of US denim behemoth Levi’s.